	<description>
		<![CDATA[<b>AutoArm</b>

<b>Core features</b>
• Add weapons to outfit filters just like apparel
• Colonists automatically equip better weapons based on their skills
• Respects player choice - manually equipped weapons are remembered

<b>How to Use</b>
1. You'll see a new "Weapons" category under Apparel
2. Allow/disallow specific weapons or entire categories
3. Colonists will automatically manage their weapons according to the policy

<b>Load Order:</b>
Loads after Core, DLCs, and framework mods (CE, Simple Sidearms, etc).
Loads before equipment management and AI behavior mods.
Auto-sort handles most cases.

Report issues at the workshop]]>
